add_dependencies_to_description
                        Searches for external packages and adds them to
                        the Imports field in the description
create_compendium       Quickly create a basic research compendium by
                        combining several rrtools functions into one.
use_analysis            Adds an analysis directory (and
                        sub-directories), and an Rmd file ready to
                        write
use_circleci            Add a circleci config file
use_compendium          Creates an R package suitable to use as a
                        research compendium, and switches to the
                        working directory of this new package, ready to
                        work
use_dockerfile          Add a Dockerfile
use_readme_rmd          Creates skeleton README files
use_travis              Add a travis config file
